<doc id="223271" wikidata="Q920266" url="?curid=223271" title="Royal Physiographic Society in Lund">
<text>The Royal Physiographic Society in Lund (), is one of the Royal Academies in Sweden. It was founded in Lund, on December 2, 1772, and received a Royal Charter by Gustav III, on March 6, 1778.

